Women\u201d category of the site.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lampen|first1=Claire |title=xHamster Launches 'Porn For Women' Fund To Help Woman-Identifying Filmmakers Get You Off |url=https://www.bustle.com/p/xhamster-launches-porn-for-women-fund-to-help-woman-identifying-filmmakers-get-you-off-10140635 |publisher=Bustle Digital Group|accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|last1=Nguyen|first1=Kristina|title=Porn site xHamster is fundraising for female adult filmmakers|url=https://www.dailydot.com/irl/xhamster-women-porn-filmmaker-fund/|publisher=Daily Dot|accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Alptraum|first1=Lux|title= What if porn, but for women |url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/9/18/17861996/porn-for-women-xhamster-grants-stipends-female-pornography|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref> According to xHamster Vice President Alex Hawkins, the goal of the fund is to increase the availability of porn that women viewers want to watch as well as to address the discrepancy between the site\u2019s visitors, 25% of whom identify as women, and the 95% of site content aimed at a male audience. <ref>{{cite web|last1=Lampen|first1=Claire |title=xHamster Launches 'Porn For Women' Fund To Help Woman-Identifying Filmmakers Get You Off |url=https://www.bustle.com/p/xhamster-launches-porn-for-women-fund-to-help-woman-identifying-filmmakers-get-you-off-10140635 |publisher=Bustle Digital Group|accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Nguyen|first1=Kristina |title=Porn site xHamster is fundraising for female adult filmmakers |url=https://www.dailydot.com/irl/xhamster-women-porn-filmmaker-fund/ |publisher=Daily Dot |accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref> Submissions were judged by \"a rotating team of women-identified judges, made up of fans, porn stars, journalists and xHamster employees.\"<ref>{{cite web|last1=Alptraum|first1=Lux |title= What if porn, but for women |url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/9/18/17861996/porn-for-women-xhamster-grants-stipends-female-pornography |publisher=Vox Media |accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref> Starting September 1, amateur and professional women-identifying filmmakers could apply for grants in the range of $500 to $10,000.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lampen|first1=Claire |title=xHamster Launches 'Porn For Women' Fund To Help Woman-Identifying Filmmakers Get You Off |url=https://www.bustle.com/p/xhamster-launches-porn-for-women-fund-to-help-woman-identifying-filmmakers-get-you-off-10140635 |publisher=Bustle Digital Group|accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Nguyen|first1=Kristina |title=Porn site xHamster is fundraising for female adult filmmakers |url=https://www.dailydot.com/irl/xhamster-women-porn-filmmaker-fund/ |publisher=Daily Dot |accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref> The films will be made available for free and without interest claims from xHamster.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lampen|first1=Claire |title=xHamster Launches 'Porn For Women' Fund To Help Woman-Identifying Filmmakers Get You Off |url=https://www.bustle.com/p/xhamster-launches-porn-for-women-fund-to-help-woman-identifying-filmmakers-get-you-off-10140635 |publisher=Bustle Digital Group|accessdate=11 April 2020 |quote=\"XHamster will not be charging viewers for the material it commissions. \"We don't ask that the content be exclusive to us or neither do we ask for any rights to it or control over it,\" Hawkins says. \"We very simply want to reward innovative and interesting filmmakers. We want to encourage people who might want to share their fantasies to do it.\"}}</ref> While other major porn sites have sought in recent years to appeal to women viewers, xHamster appears to be the first major porn site to offer monetary incentive for this.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lampen|first1=Claire |title=xHamster Launches 'Porn For Women' Fund To Help Woman-Identifying Filmmakers Get You Off |url=https://www.bustle.com/p/xhamster-launches-porn-for-women-fund-to-help-woman-identifying-filmmakers-get-you-off-10140635 |publisher=Bustle Digital Group|accessdate=11 April 2020 |quote=\"It bears noting that Pornhub, another hulking tube site and an xHamster competitor, did recently announce a similar site change. Having noted a growth spurt in its women viewership, Pornhub announced in February that it would rebrand its \"Female Friendly\" category to \"Popular With Women.\" It also solicited suggestions from users as to what type of content they really wanted to see. Pornhub did not throw money at creators, however, so in this respect, xHamster would seem to be breaking ground.\"}}</ref>\n\n==Website==\nxHamster provides various pornographic videos, photos, and [[Erotic literature|erotic stories]] grouped under categories catering to specific [[Sexual fetishism|fetishes]] or sexual preferences.<ref name=\"Rosewarne2011\">{{cite book|author=Lauren Rosewarne|title=Part-time Perverts: Sex, Pop Culture, and Kink Management|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ky_Y6KdIIBgC&pg=PA71|year=2011|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-0-313-39157-6|page=71}}</ref> Users uploading content select from a series of set categories. The most popular category, \"amateur\", tags 30% of all videos posted.<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://antonomase.fr/fi/mazieres_pornstudies_2014.pdf|page=85|doi=10.1080/23268743.2014.888214|title=Deep tags: toward a quantitative analysis of online pornography|journal=[[Porn Studies]] |volume=1|issue=1\u20132 |last1=Mazi\u00e8res|first1=Antoine |last2=Trachman|first2=Mathieu |last3=Cointet|first3=Jean-Philippe |last4=Coulmont|first4=Baptiste |last5=Prieur|first5=Christophe}}</ref> Popular gay uploads include \"big cocks\" and \"bare back\" with Oregon having the lowest gay porn view time at 1.5 hours a week while West Virginia has the highest view rate at 3.3 hours a week.<ref>{{cite web|title=Here's Everything You Need To Know About People's Gay Male Porn |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/benhenry/year-of-the-daddy|publisher=Buzz Feed|accessdate=29 September 2017}}</ref> The proportion of f